Class ListIndexesOperation<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.mongodb.operation.ListIndexesOperation<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - the operations result type.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    AsyncReadOperation<AsyncBatchCursor<T>>, ReadOperation<BatchCursor<T>>

    public class ListIndexesOperation<T>
extends Object
implements AsyncReadOperation<AsyncBatchCursor<T>>, ReadOperation<BatchCursor<T>>
    An operation that lists the indexes that have been created on a collection. For flexibility, the type of each document returned is generic.
    Since:
    3.0
    MongoDB documentation
    List indexes
